<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Property Rejected - AWARI</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .property-title {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .property-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #1e3d6f;
        }
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">AWARI</div>
            <div class="warning-icon">âœ—</div>
            <h1 class="property-title">Property Rejected</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>,</p>
            
            <p>We're writing to inform you that your property listing has been rejected after review by our team.</p>
            
            <div class="property-details">
                <h3>Property Details</h3>
                <% if (property) { %>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Property Title:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= property.title %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Address:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= property.address %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Property Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= property.propertyType %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Listing Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= property.listingType %></span>
                </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rejection-reason">
                <h4>Rejection Reason:</h4>
                <p><%= notification.message || 'Your property did not meet our quality standards. Please review the requirements and resubmit.' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>What You Can Do:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review our property listing guidelines</li>
                    <li>Update your property information based on the feedback</li>
                    <li>Add high-quality photos of your property</li>
                    <li>Ensure all required information is complete and accurate</li>
                    <li>Resubmit your property for review</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Don't worry! You can make the necessary changes and resubmit your property for review. Our team is here to help you create a successful listing.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= actionUrl || 'https://awari.com/dashboard/properties' %>" class="cta-button">
                    <%= actionText || 'Update Property' %>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions about the rejection or need assistance with improving your listing, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The AWARI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to <%= user.email %> regarding your property listing.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 AWARI. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
